speech: There are a lot of different resources available to students for help, such as; Academics, child care, clothing, food, health services, housing, legal assistance, mental health resources, transportation, utilities. You can find more specific help by following a link on this page: http://century.custhelp.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/665

At century we have a Resource and Support Center to help you become a successful and healthy student. They can help to better answer your questions. You can also find more information by following this link: http://century.custhelp.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/665
